feat: Refactor upload session model and repository methods
- Updated UploadSession model to bind with a temporary physical entity instead of a logical file. - Modified CreateUploadRequest to clarify chunk size usage. - Added FindUploadingByOwnerID method to EntityRepository to retrieve ongoing upload tasks for a user. - Implemented FindBatchByIDs method for batch retrieval of physical storage entities. - Enhanced entityRepository to support new methods and optimized existing ones. - Refactored fileEntityRepository and fileRepository for consistency and improved readability. - Updated main.go to reflect changes in service initialization.
